## Sign 4: You're Reintegrating Remote or Hybrid Employees

Remote and hybrid work is still the norm for plenty of Victoria businesses. That means you regularly have people rejoining the physical team after weeks or months apart.

Reintegration gets awkward when the only shared context is a Slack channel. People who haven't spent real time together default to surface-level small talk, and surface-level small talk doesn't build trust.

An active group event compresses that process. When everyone's physically in the same space — competing together, reacting to the same moments, cheering each other on — you can build months of passive familiarity into a couple of hours.

